{"tid":1889081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721唔見人，七個月]記唔記得仲有北角福建佬打人都係唔見人啊？","createTime":"2020-02-20T13:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T15:45:42.000Z","uid":142716,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f810bccdb458ef0101c03056319b3f63bbf2e1e","tid":1889081,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:47:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">報應啊死黑警</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n據悉，今日（20日）出現透過計劃發現的首宗初步確診個案，樣本來自觀塘協和街普通科門診的患者，消息稱，患者為一名<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">駐守北角警署</span></strong>、住在油美苑的警員，過去14日曾上班，昨日向診所提交樣本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kq7K2nK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkq7K2nK.jpg&h=e8b132b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSnK2nK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSnK2nK.jpg&h=7b2f683b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcXi6Pq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcXi6Pq.jpg&h=dec6f1b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vShbHmY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvShbHmY.jpg&h=bf9debd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190809/7QRCNAE77IZOMC5SBLKV2UZC34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190809%2F7QRCNAE77IZOMC5SBLKV2UZC34&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=4ef03a58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190809%2F7QRCNAE77IZOMC5SBLKV2UZC34&h=4fff5a95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190809/7QRCNAE77IZOMC5SBLKV2UZC34</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有，</span><br />\n同一晚有一個手足因為有<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>一個鉗同噴漆</strong></span>，<br />\n而以「意圖將其作非法用途使用」被捕後去左北角狗屋<br />\n<br />\n// 辯方作出多項投訴，包括被告錄取口供時被警員威脅「<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>好似打黑社會咁打你</strong></span>」、行使緘默權時，即<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>被便衣警員以右手打其左臉</strong></span>。有警員聲稱向他錄口供「只係傾閒計」，不會作紀錄。據悉涉事警署為北角警署。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200203/s00001/1580709256922/結他導師藏鉗涉管有攻擊武器-辯方稱被告錄口供緘默被警打臉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200203%2Fs00001%2F1580709256922%2F%E7%B5%90%E4%BB%96%E5%B0%8E%E5%B8%AB%E8%97%8F%E9%89%97%E6%B6%89%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E9%8C%84%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E7%B7%98%E9%BB%98%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%93%E8%87%89&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=983eb875\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200203%2Fs00001%2F1580709256922%2F%E7%B5%90%E4%BB%96%E5%B0%8E%E5%B8%AB%E8%97%8F%E9%89%97%E6%B6%89%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E9%8C%84%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E7%B7%98%E9%BB%98%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%93%E8%87%89&h=b14cd4d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200203/s00001/1580709256922/結他導師藏鉗涉管有攻擊武器-辯方稱被告錄口供緘默被警打臉</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月1嘅被捕手足個個走嘅時候都要著住灰色衫拖鞋咁走<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500892-20200103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500892-20200103.htm&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=493396c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500892-20200103.htm&h=581e5fc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500892-20200103.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"